Thérèse Quentin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%C3%A9r%C3%A8se_Quentin 0 Thérèse Quentin (5 July 1929 – 20 February 2015) was a French actress. She was married to the actor and stage director Marcel Cuvelier (1924–2015), with whom she had a daughter, actress Marie Cuvelier.
